{"tid":894057,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳亦凡遭美國 ITunes 刪除銷售數據　銷量榜冠軍被指造假　","createTime":"2018-11-08T06:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T07:56:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"72af93dc6d3150411d2d80e916e1e012fe76cef6","tid":894057,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"韓國男團 EXO 的前中國成員吳亦凡，於本月 2 日推出了首張個人大碟 《Antares》，在美國 iTunes 的銷量榜上名列前矛，更一度力壓 Ariana Grande 及 Lady Gaga 等天后級歌手，引發大批網民關注。其後，有傳言指吳亦凡新專輯的成績，是透過大量支持者不斷重覆購買來推高成績。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/louis-vuitton-kris-wu-ambassador-11-768x512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Flouis-vuitton-kris-wu-ambassador-11-768x512.jpg&h=b0fd0650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/tSI9B0R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FtSI9B0R.jpg&h=cf629af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國方面的 iTunes 在調查事件後，直接將吳亦凡新歌的數據清除。 Lady Gaga 及 Ariana Grande 重回銷量榜冠軍及亞軍地位。Ariana Grande 的經理人被指發文投訴吳亦凡使用作弊手段推高銷量成績，但他其後於 Twitter 上發文否認有關言論。有傳 Ariana Grande 也讚好了諷刺吳亦凡的貼文，甚有火藥味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/k5mnzeO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fk5mnzeO.jpg&h=bfbfddc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《網易》報道，吳亦凡支持者事前經過多月準備，當專輯正式推出後，就不斷切換帳號重覆購買。務求做出最驚人的成績。但現時 Apple 方面已刪去新專輯所有銷售數據了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/oI2A96I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FoI2A96I.jpg&h=25ebe15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/11/07/kris-wu/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F11%2F07%2Fkris-wu%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=Ka4QYMh6GiHTsAA8ISVHEoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=3c93de7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/11/07/kris-wu/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"b79c9705c35749caf5d9e41c7248830cf1e123b0","tid":894057,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:04:34.000Z","msg":"skr~~"},{"pid":"d6d4b079269a12b47aa7f6a7e0eb14f89b383526","tid":894057,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"重複購買係真係有俾錢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f38feea96c5bfac9bbb1249a1d3ba2cdfac92c","tid":894057,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:24:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c14aa886d03eea7ea5dad55bbe27fb9b5586156","tid":894057,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1652ceb8cf3c6bc546d06c734d4dc49b22f3779a","tid":894057,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0aaf4cd7f83791ac0e24ab6ee8eb905941c272e","tid":894057,"uid":65604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:36:40.000Z","msg":"如果個蘋果收左錢又無回到水，咁個交易真係堅喎，akb個d都係一箱一箱咁買(不過係實體) ，其實點計數？"},{"pid":"bb9d5f4